{"data": {"__GLOBAL": {"_ATTACH_BASE_VIEW": "img.nga.178.com/attachments"}, "__U": {"150058": {"uid": 150058, "username": "UID:150058", "credit": 135537154, "medal": "272,207,157,92", "reputation": "28_30,61_0,147_775,130_10", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 73, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1123989606, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 41083, "rvrc": 29, "money": 90765, "thisvisit": 1782044211, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 135537154}, "39248719": {"uid": 39248719, "username": "UID:39248719", "credit": 169222721, "medal": null, "reputation": "61_233,85_15,70_15,133_15,137_15,246_15,-7_30,147_-585,268_15", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1476240137, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 626, "rvrc": 11, "money": 50500, "thisvisit": 1782023711, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 169222721, "buffs": {"120": [[1616711, 120, 39248719, 39248719, 1762390528, 1856998528, 7, 1, "", "..res.."]]}}, "62824316": {"uid": 62824316, "username": "UID:62824316", "credit": 169083392, "medal": null, "reputation": "61_23,246_15,22_30,147_-600", "groupid": -1, "memberid": 39, "avatar": null, "yz": 4, "site": null, "honor": null, "regdate": 1608745419, "mute_time": null, "postnum": 760, "rvrc": 10, "money": 1900, "thisvisit": 1776504353, "signature": null, "nickname": null, "bit_data": 169083392}, "__GROUPS": {"73": ["学徒", 360672, 73], "39": ["学徒", 98528, 39]}, "__MEDALS": {"272": ["272.gif", "棒棒糖", "叔叔请你吃棒棒糖", 272], "207": ["207.gif", "爆竹声中旧岁除", "一支红杏出墙来", 207], "157": ["157.gif", "王者之剑", "王者之剑活动纪念", 157], "92": ["92.gif", "小心死亡之翼-", "2011年大灾变开服纪念", 92]}, "__REPUTATIONS": {"147": {"150058": 775, "39248719": -585, "62824316": -600, "0": "大时代"}}}, "__R": [{"content": "我重申一下<br/>我唯一就在这里开帖子聊，没有任何别的渠道，也没有任何账号分享，平时不看消息，除非有深度的研究分享。<br/>所说的仅仅是我自己的个人看法和操作，不做任何的指导 带教等等。<br/>如果你们有逻辑的分享可以讨论，不单纯讨论个股。<br/>旧的帖子在[url]https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?tid=43098323[/url]<br/>[url]https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?tid=45922084[/url]<br/>里面有一些经验分享。但不重要<br/><br/><br/>让我们坚持科技是第一生产力，人才是第一资源，创新是第一动力的核心思想，手握科技核心，学习股票技术，打造自己的操作体系，最终走向财富自由的康庄大道", "alterinfo": "\t[A600 0 6 63539820 长期答疑解惑奖励]", "tid": 45974302, "score": 570, "score_2": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 09:05", "authorid": 150058, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "type": 33554468, "fid": 706, "pid": 0, "recommend": 0, "lou": 0, "content_length": 412, "comment_id": ["854270755", "860174433"], "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241578,64199867,11586486,5641907,66685489,66633842,65208818,42941765,,42964685,42181525,14317962,67086252,34699482,62593385,67000864,64005788,62799978,60424140,42468630,61560061,67096060,61021164,67102441,63220970,19312329,60694817,67086969,67061200,60701305,66937546,62357329,41746951,60027718,,39248719,62403348,40776497,67088120,66875016,64268963,1459804,67062343,12177085,38702942,1383368,67093370,66885146,40024017,63922791,67095295,66895557,64571355,62824316,5495109,38806682,67122547,67137453,67078475,,38110681,66618696,64658121,67085304,38883076,67132556,67126715,62653482,67128658,64731349,67105996,65464857,67143142,67118412,36620789,62234787,67115759,67136133,2062702,4627122,67095345,67145169,67105952,67054948,67085379,66758380,43207490,37784933,19483255,34874814,37791497,14884234,64997287,63841614,8555597,67098132,62368609,39205700,42258905,61649350,1224802,41288139,67150573,60252995,66801275,2251556,66907545,67004473,67088624,67103794,42700304,67193496,40810297,67210279,,64942487,1134755,60347315,67236214,66144535,63849256", "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768179906, "comment": [{"pid": 854270755, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 39248719, "type": 1, "score": 3, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 09:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[b]Reply to [tid=45974302]Topic[/tid] Post by [uid=150058]-阿狼-[/uid] (2026-01-12 09:05)[/b]<br/><br/>遇到自爆卡车一定不要回复！不要引用！点右下角+号，再选择举报，举报有奖励！", "lou": 0, "content_length": 73, "comment_to_id": -1, "from_client": "8 Android", "postdatetimestamp": 1768180232}, {"pid": 860174433, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 62824316, "type": 1, "score": 161, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-03-06 00:35", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "[E1772820633 0 0]\t", "content": "[b]Reply to [tid=45974302]Topic[/tid] Post by [uid=150058]-阿狼-[/uid] (2026-01-12 09:05)[/b]<br/><br/>好用的计算器：<br/>娜美版：[url=https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?pid=859773354&amp;opt=128]36516楼[/url]特点：娜美不断更新逻辑，只需要关注此楼层即可<br/>xhox版：[url=https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?pid=860287572&amp;opt=128]41494楼[/url] 特点：隐藏了一些无用指标，更简洁好用，深色主题(已更新)<br/>大时代冲冲冲版：[url=https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?pid=860150282&amp;opt=128]39975楼[/url]特点：带持仓排序，20s刷新行情，有模拟仓功能<br/>拉法github版：[url=https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?pid=860167314&amp;opt=128]40134楼[/url]特点：有狼大逻辑和海指导逻辑两套方案<br/>大建荒文版：[url=https://bbs.nga.cn/read.php?pid=860171791&amp;opt=128]40178楼[/url] 特点：有日线图+定时器", "lou": 0, "content_length": 384, "comment_to_id": -1, "14": {"14": 1}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1772728556}]}, {"pid": 854270131, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 53, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 09:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "先拿一个前排编辑", "lou": 1, "content_length": 16, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768179937}, {"pid": 854271001, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 79, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 09:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854270386,45974302,3]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60027718]xiaomiwang1[/uid] (2026-01-12 09:07):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，仓位之前因为贪心想吃差价减了太多的话，需要在震荡里补齐仓位吗，是不是不可以为了贪等太深的回踩[/quote]<br/>低开 缩量  急跳水 拉回平盘附近 盘中再次翻绿，这种就是可以打进去了 这种就是比较确定性的机会了<br/>其他的话可以通过不断的日内做T把仓位打进去  或者和我一样  把半导体的钱出去航天和AI打野，相当于多赚5个点10个点  然后赚完直接回去，等于又把半导体成本拉低5个点。<br/>所以能不能买看你自己的能力，像龟哥那些我都是建议他躺死，3-3躺到我说结束。他就不挣这个差价", "lou": 2, "content_length": 331, "reply_to": 854270386, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768180358}, {"pid": 854276018, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 40, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 09:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "刚才指数盘中翻绿了  有没有加一点设备", "lou": 3, "content_length": 34, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768182839}, {"pid": 854276336, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 20, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 09:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854275912,45974302,14]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60898007]年轻的z老头[/uid] (2026-01-12 09:53):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，请问下航天现在这么涨还会有二波三波的预期吗？或者说会把二波三波的高度空间挤压掉吗？[/quote]<br/>第一波都没完  走完了后才能算幅度  每一波都是分开的  万一调整很深呢。", "lou": 4, "content_length": 67, "reply_to": 854275912, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768182985}, {"pid": 854276564, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 60, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 09:58", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "早说一次  航天和AI应用按每天都是最后一天来做。板块出现问题就出场 不然就拿着<br/>但是半导体是我的趋势长线，打野的钱一定会回去的。", "lou": 5, "content_length": 120, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768183097}, {"pid": 854278457, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 78, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 10:12", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "量在放不是很正常。你们看看是不是4006在确认的那几天不断放量 确认后加速放量<br/>这是市场踏空资金在确认后的进场条件，达成条件 然后进场，这是一个非常正常的事情。<br/>只是现在进场的资金全冲了AI应用和航天，那旧时代的海外链没有消息刺激的情况下被暂时放弃了而已<br/><br/>今天的利好就是 鲍鲍被查  全球迎接 [color=red][size=150%]大放水时代[/size][/color]", "lou": 6, "content_length": 272, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768183929}, {"pid": 854281607, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 54, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 10:34", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "中场有获利卖盘是正常的，只要买盘不减少就行，外面踏空的和场内没涨踏空这15连阳的不在少数。有量就有价", "lou": 7, "content_length": 98, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768185265}, {"pid": 854286576, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 11:07", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854285447,45974302,22]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=61422464]kaiserDu[/uid] (2026-01-12 11:00):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，半岛铁盒目前看盘中调整的概率好大，没啥大利空的话，感觉1.7左右短期够呛啊~[/quote]<br/>我说了 利用盘中大盘带下来的机会做正T 要么就平躺。", "lou": 8, "content_length": 52, "reply_to": 854285447, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768187254}, {"pid": 854286995, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 8, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 11:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854285700,45974302,23]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43068033]aec2018[/uid] (2026-01-12 11:02):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，怎么看北方稀土。打算拿100个做长线[/quote]<br/>现在我不看稀土 我之前用的BYD换的稀土目前都25%以上盈利了  这些东西我不动的", "lou": 9, "content_length": 75, "reply_to": 854285700, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768187400}, {"pid": 854287734, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 10, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 11:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854287271,45974302,24]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=14884234]躺平任嘲[/uid] (2026-01-12 11:11):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，如果正式要进入大放水时代的话，有色这边是不是也可以逢低买入ETF同样作为长持开躺的逻辑呢？[/quote]<br/>有色还有低位？", "lou": 10, "content_length": 19, "reply_to": 854287271, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768187677}, {"pid": 854287828, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 11:15", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854287689,45974302,24]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66904030]萌萌521121[/uid] (2026-01-12 11:14):[/b]<br/><br/>报告狼大，稀土鸡已经25个点，稀土游戏都是按照狼大说的长拿。[/quote]<br/>嗯 稀土 游戏 不要看他就对了 看了什么时候都想卖", "lou": 11, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 854287689, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768187713}, {"pid": 854289911, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 24, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 11:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854288330,45974302,25]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=14884234]躺平任嘲[/uid] (2026-01-12 11:18):[/b]<br/><br/>ETF不是个股啊，如果说这都算高位的话，那半导体也是高位，那为何放水逻辑不能适用于同样受益的有色这边呢，求解[/quote]<br/>我没说放水逻辑不适合有色啊  有色肯定是第一受益<br/>但是我做期货那边的 我不做股票的有色", "lou": 12, "content_length": 83, "reply_to": 854288330, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768188456}, {"pid": 854298595, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 202, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 12:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "现在你们是不是怕加速赶顶 然后怕自己手里面的票和大盘一起泥沙俱下？怕自己的票涨的时候涨不过大盘，也没拿目前的两大题材，不敢追的同时还怕暴跌？<br/>如果是的话我收盘后或者晚上复盘了和你们说一下这种时候的对应方式<br/>然后还有你们是不是一到这种时候就忘记之前分享过的盘中做T策略了？就是急 虽然不知道急什么 但是就是很焦虑 。", "lou": 13, "content_length": 301, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768192326}, {"pid": 854299741, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 79, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 12:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854299435,45974302,30]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66920942]飞火扑流萤[/uid] (2026-01-12 12:39):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大现在就说吧 下午收盘完怕来不及了[/quote]<br/>看吧 我就说了 现在你们就是急<br/>急什么呢 指数支撑破位了吗 从放量转缩量了吗  高标板块爆了吗 期指空单猛加了吗 30年债放量暴涨了吗 券商砸破位了吗 有什么迹象表明要崩了吗", "lou": 14, "content_length": 155, "reply_to": 854299435, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768192920}, {"pid": 854301174, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 12:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们不敢看盘的 去思考一下 之前的判断<br/>3-2的结束确认条件是什么  日线级别W底后的红三兵表现  突破颈线的加速  4006站稳三天后量能的暴涨  吃技术流和踏空资金的进场溢价<br/>这些都是一步步来的，现在躺吃溢价的时候，为什么要怕啊。。<br/>而且3-2吃的利润拿来干嘛的  就是拿来3-3不要盘中操作，哪怕死也要看收盘位置的底气啊。。。。<br/><br/><br/>你怕什么 <br/>怕赚钱吗", "lou": 15, "content_length": 306, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768193731}, {"pid": 854303648, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 32, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 13:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854303500,45974302,34]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=9032340]letuswowing[/uid] (2026-01-12 13:18):[/b]<br/><br/>有人已经开始抢跑了[s:ac:哭笑][s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>获利盘卖盘这有啥啊。。。涨那么多有人卖不是正常的？你看有没有人接盘就行了  量还在不在就行。外面踏空的多少人懂不", "lou": 16, "content_length": 113, "reply_to": 854303500, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768195219}, {"pid": 854304969, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 13:32", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854304451,45974302,35]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=9032340]letuswowing[/uid] (2026-01-12 13:28):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大 没有看空<br/>有没有可能高标跳水后日内就流入其他板块 还是跳水就大盘跟着一起下去 然后调整后再选择板块？[/quote]<br/>你是不是看超人片看多了   你能不能从一辆高速行驶的车上直接跳到应急车道慢速行驶的车上而不死？<br/>唯一活着的可能就是  这慢速的车加速赶上  你才能有机会跳过去", "lou": 17, "content_length": 147, "reply_to": 854304451, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768195964}, {"pid": 854305930, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 63, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 13:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854305617,45974302,35]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60608517]Jerowe[/uid] (2026-01-12 13:39):[/b]<br/><br/>很形象了 航天都是压监管 蓝标主动进[/quote]<br/>你就这么想就行了  当时AI硬的钱是怎么出去的 你们老是觉得这些高的就要去那些低位没起来的<br/>但是实际是什么  是商业航天加速起来才吃了AI硬的钱，那能接力商业航天的不就是下一个加速的AI软，AIDC，还有分散出来核聚变等等<br/>这些钱会去白酒吗 地产吗？会去那些没起来的吗？不会的。风偏就不一样。", "lou": 18, "content_length": 271, "reply_to": 854305617, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768196520}, {"pid": 854307033, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-01-12 13:52", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=854306861,45974302,36]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66515200]arikon[/uid] (2026-01-12 13:51):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，我的思考是：大盘延续周五的高潮，双雄带着飞。细看航天里面异动触发监管的已经很多了，今晚批量异动监管名单。AI继续全体高潮，明天应该是个降温日。所以今天没追高的，也可以等一下看明天分歧再上车[/quote]<br/>不追高没问题啊 是对的啊  问题是无理由看空的。", "lou": 19, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 854306861, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1768197175}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155634, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782111176, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "yuzuhikari", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782111191, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241578,64199867,11586486,5641907,66685489,66633842,65208818,42941765,,42964685,42181525,14317962,67086252,34699482,62593385,67000864,64005788,62799978,60424140,42468630,61560061,67096060,61021164,67102441,63220970,19312329,60694817,67086969,67061200,60701305,66937546,62357329,41746951,600